   165→function arrayChainable
   177→/**
   178→ * `P.optional(subpattern)` takes a sub pattern and returns a pattern which matches if the
   179→ * key is undefined or if it is defined and the sub pattern matches its value.
   180→ *
   181→ * [Read the documentation for `P.optional` on GitHub](https://github.com/gvergnaud/ts-pattern#poptional-patterns)
